{"tid":2056624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一週年】一人一個呢一年黎既得著","createTime":"2020-06-08T23:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T02:28:15.000Z","uid":60539,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c5e28f67810c9622c2e15d81800102e9d1f98e7f","tid":2056624,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:42:17.000Z","msg":"1. 發覺香港人唔係大家口中成日講既垃圾，只係大家慣左上一代果種鬧你都係為你好既心態<br />\n<br />\n2. 對香港人既身份有強烈認同，作為香港人感到非常光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 全世界都知香港係咩地方，唔洗自我介紹講完 I come from Hong Kong 之後要再解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 佩服香港人，可以係一年內令中共多次柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 發覺香港人好有愛，超越左班廢老成日懷緬既鄰里關係，係街上任何一個陌生既同路人都可以無條件守望相助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 香港人既靈活變通唔係流，由百萬人上街到登報，再有黃色經濟圈，期待大家再發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 00後唔再係一個負面標簽，曾經好擔心00後會全面赤化，但呢一年完全刮目相看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. 學識左無視五毛挑釁既留言，留低負評就算，唔會覆佢比佢spin走個討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c5ebe9dc5d59d5a3917fe6cd6aa380f4f544b6","tid":2056624,"uid":268271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:43:44.000Z","msg":"民主覺醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc51ce550055a5b3db5b3b519070b7e22fecac5","tid":2056624,"uid":65091,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T23:43:56.000Z","msg":"10. 唔好對港豬有任何期望，例如罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c823149e6ba00ecf7ad994399ac165368edc5c","tid":2056624,"uid":60539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91c5ebe9dc5d59d5a3917fe6cd6aa380f4f544